			event-block is sunflower
		then:
			add 24*{miningmultiplier::%player's uuid%} to {miningxp::%player's uuid%}
			send action bar "&a[+%(24*{miningmultiplier::%player's uuid%})% exp (%{miningxp::%player's uuid%}%/%{miningxpreq::%player's uuid%}%)]" to player
